plague-forced-vomit-name = Nausea attack
plague-forced-vomit-desc = Allows you to force an infected victim to vomit the contents of their stomach.

plague-asthmatic-name = Asthma attack
plague-asthmatic-desc = Allows you to induce an asthma attack in a victim, hindering their breathing for a short time.

plague-dizziness-name = Dizziness
plague-dizziness-desc = Allows you to intoxicate a victim, blurring their vision.

plague-sleepy-name = Drowsiness
plague-sleepy-desc = Allows you to force a victim to fall asleep for a short duration.

plague-rat-name = Rat fuss I
plague-rat-desc = Allows you to transform into an infectious rat to spread the plague.

plague-rats-name = Rat fust II
plague-rats-desc = Upon transforming into a rat, several more rats appear near you.

plague-slimes-name = Slime-blob
plague-slimes-desc = Allows you to drop plague slimes at a designated point.

plague-bugs-name = Insect swarm
plague-bugs-desc = Allows you to drop a swarm of plague insects at a designated point.

plague-tp-sick-name = Teleport to sick
plague-tp-sick-desc = Allows you to teleport to a random infected individual.

plague-tp-not-sick-name = Teleport to healthy
plague-tp-not-sick-desc = Allows you to teleport to a random uninfected humanoid.

plague-cataract-name = Cataract
plague-cataract-desc = Allows you to permanently damage a victim's eyesight, but not completely deprive them of it.

plague-injury-name = Open wounds
plague-injury-desc = Allows you to cause extremely severe bleeding in a victim.

plague-heart-name = Black mark
plague-heart-desc = Allows you to induce a fatal heart attack in a victim.